name: Janitor
description:
janitor is about joe, a recent highschool flunk working a dead end janitor gig, one day he gets called in to clean up a house, his task is to clean up garbage and put away tools and make sure the place is spotless. what sort of consequences will arise if you cant help joe clean up in time?
